<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>4</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="適切な頭皮ケア方法"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E9.81.A9.E5.88.87.E3.81.AA.E9.A0.AD.E7.9A.AE.E3.82.B1.E3.82.A2.E6.96.B9.E6.B3.95"><div class="method_label">方法 4 の 24:</div>適切な頭皮ケア方法</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_4" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-310">
<a name="step_4_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-11-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 11というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/96/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d6e48f91ef5f730f636243141412ad28" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/96/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('d6e48f91ef5f730f636243141412ad28')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 11というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/96/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/96/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d6e48f91ef5f730f636243141412ad28"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/9\/96\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/9\/96\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-11-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">髪は洗い過ぎに留意しながら定期的に洗います。</b>フケは頭皮の皮膚細胞が死んで剥がれ落ちたものです。髪の毛そのものはフケの原因ではありません。
<ul>
<li>アメリカのあるクリニックでは、フケが治まるまではフケ用シャンプーで毎日洗髪し、その後、週に2～3回フケ防止シャンプーを使用することを勧めています。<sup id="_ref-1" class="reference trusted" aria-label="参考文献1へのリンク"><a href="#_note-1">[1]</a><span class="ts_popup trustedsource" hidden id="ts_popup_1" style="display: none;">
	<span class="ts_close">X</span>
		<a class="ts_trustworthy" href="/wikiHow:Delivering-a-Trustworthy-Experience">信頼性の高い出典文献</a>

		<span class="ts_name">Mayo Clinic</span>

				<a href="#" class="ts_source" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener">出典を見る</a>
</span>
</sup>
</li>
<li>洗い過ぎ、特に、ラウリル硫酸ナトリウムのような強力な化学成分を含むシャンプーを使用して過度に洗髪すると、頭皮が炎症を起こして乾燥するので、フケが増える恐れがあります。　　</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-311">
<a name="step_4_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-12-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 12というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/cd/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="70ce78ea0b5c4792f725153e2371783e" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/cd/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('70ce78ea0b5c4792f725153e2371783e')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 12というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/cd/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/cd/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="70ce78ea0b5c4792f725153e2371783e"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/cd\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/cd\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-12-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">フケ用シャンプーの効果が浸透するのを待ちます。</b>フケ用シャンプーで洗髪する際には、髪や頭皮に付けた後、5分ほどおいてから洗い流します。こうすると、シャンプーのフケ取り効果がよく働きます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-312">
<a name="step_4_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-13-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 13というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/41/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="bd8206332be1c943b80f49ae1ac356da" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/41/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('bd8206332be1c943b80f49ae1ac356da')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 13というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/41/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/41/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="bd8206332be1c943b80f49ae1ac356da"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/4\/41\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/4\/41\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-13-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">シャンプー後にブラシで髪をとかし、フケを防止します。</b>髪をとかすと頭皮や髪の自然な油分が頭全体に行き渡ります。<sup id="_ref-2" class="reference" aria-label="参考文献2へのリンク"><a href="#_note-2">[2]</a><span class="ts_popup " hidden id="ts_popup_2" style="display: none;">
	<span class="ts_close">X</span>
		<span class="ts_name">出典文献</span>
		<span class="ts_description"></span>
				<a href="#" class="ts_source" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"></a>

</span>
</sup>
<ul><li>頭皮から毛先に向かってブラシをかけて、頭皮の油分を全体に行き渡らせます。　</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-313">
<a name="step_4_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-14-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 14というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="098829cee462591be23b205dc673f0ff" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('098829cee462591be23b205dc673f0ff')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 14というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="098829cee462591be23b205dc673f0ff"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/d\/d6\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/d\/d6\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-14-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ストレスやストレスのかかる状況を避けます。</b>フケはストレスによっても出るので、ストレスがかからないようにする、または健康的で効果的な方法でストレスを解消します。
<ul>
<li>健康的な食生活を送りましょう。体内に取り込むものに体は反応します。不健康な食べ物（ファストフードや甘い物など）を食べ過ぎると、肌、頭皮、髪にトラブルが起こりがちです。</li>
<li>亜鉛やビタミンB6が豊富な食品は特に、頭皮や髪の健康を保つのに重要です。　</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
