<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>5</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="フェヌグリークシード"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.95.E3.82.A7.E3.83.8C.E3.82.B0.E3.83.AA.E3.83.BC.E3.82.AF.E3.82.B7.E3.83.BC.E3.83.89"><div class="method_label">方法 5 の 24:</div>フェヌグリークシード</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_5" class="section_text">
<p class="steps_text healthintro">フェヌグリークシードはフケ取りに最適です。
</p>
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-414">
<a name="step_5_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-15-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 15というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-15-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-15-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0522d93530675d1fcf7b70dae1388c3b" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-15-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-15-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('0522d93530675d1fcf7b70dae1388c3b')</script>
