<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>6</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ベビーオイル"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.99.E3.83.93.E3.83.BC.E3.82.AA.E3.82.A4.E3.83.AB"><div class="method_label">方法 6 の 24:</div>ベビーオイル</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_6" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-518">
<a name="step_6_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-19-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
