<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 19というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/fe/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/fe/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="b35659bf2abb72802e2428b46588efde"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/fe\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/fe\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-19-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">頭皮にベビーオイルを塗ります。</b>ベビーオイルは少量でよく伸びます。力を入れ過ぎないように、優しく頭皮をマッサージします。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-519">
<a name="step_6_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-20-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 20というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9e149570711e2704391ddddc68e4f6b7" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('9e149570711e2704391ddddc68e4f6b7')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 20というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9e149570711e2704391ddddc68e4f6b7"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/b2\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/b2\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-20-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">タオルで髪を覆い、ベビーオイルを付けたまま一晩過ごします。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-520">
<a name="step_6_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-21-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
