</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 21というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/10/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/10/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="493e568a325561a5e1e25bf55cfeca65"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/1\/10\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/1\/10\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-21-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">翌朝、効果の高いフケ取りシャンプーで洗髪します。</b>寝ている間にオイルが頭皮の状態を整えます。
</div>
