<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>7</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="重曹"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E9.87.8D.E6.9B.B9"><div class="method_label">方法 7 の 24:</div>重曹</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_7" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-621">
<a name="step_7_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-22-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 22というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0cfcd27d282a55a5e74e8f1796adadfa" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('0cfcd27d282a55a5e74e8f1796adadfa')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 22というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0cfcd27d282a55a5e74e8f1796adadfa"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/73\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/73\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-22-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">シャンプーの代わりに一掴みの重曹を使用します。</b>重曹には様々な用途があり、天然のフケ取りとしての効用もうたわれています。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-622">
<a name="step_7_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-23-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 23というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="edb039fdd71a23a150b4aaffa792c42e" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('edb039fdd71a23a150b4aaffa792c42e')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 23というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="edb039fdd71a23a150b4aaffa792c42e"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/02\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/02\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-23-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">シャンプーの代わりに、大さじ山盛り1杯の重曹を濡らした髪と頭皮にすり込みます。</b>1分おいて、丁寧に洗い流します。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-623">
<a name="step_7_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-24-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 24というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="bd8eb8e46a4bb8906d6da6bb95d737ec" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('bd8eb8e46a4bb8906d6da6bb95d737ec')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 24というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b2/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="bd8eb8e46a4bb8906d6da6bb95d737ec"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/b2\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/b2\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-24-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">重曹の効果が現れるまで待ちます。</b>重曹でのシャンプーを2週間続けると、頭皮が自然な油分を分泌するようになり、その油分が頭皮を保湿してフケを止めます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
