<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>8</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="レモン果汁と凝乳"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.AC.E3.83.A2.E3.83.B3.E6.9E.9C.E6.B1.81.E3.81.A8.E5.87.9D.E4.B9.B3"><div class="method_label">方法 8 の 24:</div>レモン果汁と凝乳</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_8" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-724">
<a name="step_8_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-25-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 25というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/ee/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="01972aa7715d6bbd043f776e5a1611bb" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/ee/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('01972aa7715d6bbd043f776e5a1611bb')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 25というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/ee/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/ee/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="01972aa7715d6bbd043f776e5a1611bb"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/ee\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/ee\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-25-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ボウル1杯の凝乳と、半分に切ったレモン1個を用意します。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-725">
<a name="step_8_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-26-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 26というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-26-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-26-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="188ab37acc7be1183ac6413f7c88243f" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ca/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-26-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-26-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('188ab37acc7be1183ac6413f7c88243f')</script>
