<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>9</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="重曹とレモン"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E9.87.8D.E6.9B.B9.E3.81.A8.E3.83.AC.E3.83.A2.E3.83.B3"><div class="method_label">方法 9 の 24:</div>重曹とレモン</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_9" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-830">
<a name="step_9_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-31-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 31というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="95c0c88179ab0707464e5a7496585cc5" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('95c0c88179ab0707464e5a7496585cc5')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 31というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="95c0c88179ab0707464e5a7496585cc5"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/d\/d7\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/d\/d7\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-31-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">搾りたてのレモン果汁と重曹を混ぜます。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-831">
<a name="step_9_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-32-Version-5.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 32というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/03/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a4b62b7810e80c1805b51ca104336851" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/03/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('a4b62b7810e80c1805b51ca104336851')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 32というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/03/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/03/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a4b62b7810e80c1805b51ca104336851"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/03\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/03\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-32-Version-5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">混ぜたものを頭皮に塗ります。</b>数分おきます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-832">
<a name="step_9_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-33-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
