</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 33というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/a1/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-33-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-33-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a1/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-33-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-33-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9cadf658407012379bf2de256200cce3"></noscript>
