<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">頭皮が痒くなってきたら洗い流します。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-833">
<a name="step_9_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-34-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
