<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>10</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ココナッツオイル"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.82.B3.E3.82.B3.E3.83.8A.E3.83.83.E3.83.84.E3.82.AA.E3.82.A4.E3.83.AB"><div class="method_label">方法 10 の 24:</div>ココナッツオイル</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_10" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-934">
<a name="step_10_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-35-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 35というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="7f960472574f5d0b32a5a1226521e8d2" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('7f960472574f5d0b32a5a1226521e8d2')</script>
