<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 35というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="7f960472574f5d0b32a5a1226521e8d2"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f7\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f7\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-35-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">髪を洗いますが、コンディショナー類は使用しません。</b>シャワーが済んだら髪を乾かします。髪を、滑りが悪くて乾いた状態にします。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-935">
<a name="step_10_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-36-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 36というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/ae/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="610252e426578904f9bfbe13e34a1b9b" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/ae/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('610252e426578904f9bfbe13e34a1b9b')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 36というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/ae/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/ae/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="610252e426578904f9bfbe13e34a1b9b"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/a\/ae\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/ae\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-36-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ココナッツオイルを、髪の他の部分に付けないように気を付けながら頭皮に塗ります。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-936">
<a name="step_10_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-37-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 37というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9b/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dd570b2e2f0f0174f42b0afe5c34e80e" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/9b/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('dd570b2e2f0f0174f42b0afe5c34e80e')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 37というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/9b/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9b/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dd570b2e2f0f0174f42b0afe5c34e80e"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/9\/9b\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/9\/9b\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-37-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ココナッツオイルを洗い流します。</b>必ずオイルを完全に洗い流します。2回洗う必要があるかもしれませんが、通常は1度で十分でしょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-937">
<a name="step_10_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-38-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
