<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>11</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ティーツリーオイル"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.86.E3.82.A3.E3.83.BC.E3.83.84.E3.83.AA.E3.83.BC.E3.82.AA.E3.82.A4.E3.83.AB"><div class="method_label">方法 11 の 24:</div>ティーツリーオイル</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_11" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1038">
<a name="step_11_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-39-Version-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 39というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fdccf1efafc18f57ba2501ac7a3d0cd6" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/4e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('fdccf1efafc18f57ba2501ac7a3d0cd6')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 39というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/4e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fdccf1efafc18f57ba2501ac7a3d0cd6"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/4\/4e\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/4\/4e\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-39-Version-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ティーツリーオイル入りシャンプーを購入し頻繁に使用します。</b>ティーツリーオイルは香りの良い、天然の殺菌剤です。ティーツリーオイルが少なくとも5％配合されたシャンプーであれば、フケ取り効果も高いことが明らかになっています。<sup id="_ref-3" class="reference" aria-label="参考文献3へのリンク"><a href="#_note-3">[3]</a><span class="ts_popup " hidden id="ts_popup_3" style="display: none;">
