<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>12</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="マウスウオッシュ"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.9E.E3.82.A6.E3.82.B9.E3.82.A6.E3.82.AA.E3.83.83.E3.82.B7.E3.83.A5"><div class="method_label">方法 12 の 24:</div>マウスウオッシュ</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_12" class="section_text">
<p class="steps_text healthintro">月に1度行えばフケを予防できる、健康的な方法です。
</p>
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1141">
<a name="step_12_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-42-Version-4.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 42というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fbe4e06108001c21ce01cf01d9a0a087" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/5e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('fbe4e06108001c21ce01cf01d9a0a087')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 42というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/5e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fbe4e06108001c21ce01cf01d9a0a087"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/5\/5e\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/5\/5e\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-42-Version-4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">マウスウオッシュと水を１：９の割合で混ぜます。</b>普段通りに髪を洗った後、髪に注ぎます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1142">
<a name="step_12_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-43-Version-4.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
