</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 43というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c7/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="62f77a86962344ae2700fb0013200e58"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/c7\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/c7\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-43-Version-4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">混合液を頭からかけるだけです。</b>それから、普段通りに髪を整えます。洗い流してはいけません。
</div>
