<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>13</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="アップルサイダービネガー"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.82.A2.E3.83.83.E3.83.97.E3.83.AB.E3.82.B5.E3.82.A4.E3.83.80.E3.83.BC.E3.83.93.E3.83.8D.E3.82.AC.E3.83.BC"><div class="method_label">方法 13 の 24:</div>アップルサイダービネガー</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_13" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1243">
<a name="step_13_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-44-Version-4.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 44というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/2f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dc4b62b7968ac0fcfb8fe01bea5d9a88" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/2f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('dc4b62b7968ac0fcfb8fe01bea5d9a88')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 44というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/2f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/2f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dc4b62b7968ac0fcfb8fe01bea5d9a88"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/2\/2f\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/2\/2f\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-44-Version-4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">アップルサイダービネガーと水を１：１の割合で混ぜます。</b>普段通りに髪を洗い、混合液を注意深く髪に注いで頭皮にすり込みます。液が目に入らないように気を付けましょう。乾癬、完治していないひっかき傷、かさぶたなどがあるとかなり沁みます（沁みて痛いときは水で洗い流します）。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1244">
<a name="step_13_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-45-Version-4.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 45というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e4083fc4387e9d184cbab70762434c58" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('e4083fc4387e9d184cbab70762434c58')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 45というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/02/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e4083fc4387e9d184cbab70762434c58"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/02\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/02\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-45-Version-4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">10～15分おいてから水で洗い流します。</b>酢の臭いは髪が乾くと消えます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
