<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/2\/2b\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-46-Version-3.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-46-Version-3.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/2\/2b\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-46-Version-3.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-46-Version-3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">1週間ほど毎日繰り返します。</b>
</div>
