<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>16</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="バナナと酢"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.90.E3.83.8A.E3.83.8A.E3.81.A8.E9.85.A2"><div class="method_label">方法 16 の 24:</div>バナナと酢</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_16" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1551">
<a name="step_16_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-52-Version-3.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 52というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1b48b3903857900394c9208efedfc038" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/6a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('1b48b3903857900394c9208efedfc038')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 52というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/6a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1b48b3903857900394c9208efedfc038"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/6\/6a\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/6\/6a\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-52-Version-3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">バナナの皮をむきます。</b>2カップの酢に混ぜます。
<ul><li>完全に混ざり合うまでかき混ぜます。ペースト状にするにはフォークや泡だて器を使うといいでしょう。</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1552">
<a name="step_16_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-53-Version-3.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 53というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/83/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0b197d34fa24d16ec121b6f7a95064ee" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/83/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('0b197d34fa24d16ec121b6f7a95064ee')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 53というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/83/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/83/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0b197d34fa24d16ec121b6f7a95064ee"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/8\/83\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/8\/83\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-53-Version-3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ペーストを髪に塗ります。</b>頭皮に浸透するように丹念にマッサージをします。5～10分、もしくは、髪がまんべんなくペーストで覆われるまで続けます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1553">
<a name="step_16_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-54-Version-3.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 54というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/cf/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9571f8abfaefd4ef82fec69483b2d408" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/cf/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('9571f8abfaefd4ef82fec69483b2d408')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 54というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/cf/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/cf/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9571f8abfaefd4ef82fec69483b2d408"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/cf\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/cf\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-54-Version-3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">15～20分おきます。</b>それからペーストを完全に洗い流します。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1554">
<a name="step_16_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-55-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
