</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 55というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/9e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-55-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-55-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9e/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-55-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-55-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9e221f95defc4fef905ab4c7d0a85795"></noscript>
