<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>17</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="重曹と酢"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E9.87.8D.E6.9B.B9.E3.81.A8.E9.85.A2"><div class="method_label">方法 17 の 24:</div>重曹と酢</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_17" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1655">
<a name="step_17_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-56-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 56というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/44/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d26affc75707d5fae5ef98e1239cbec1" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/44/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('d26affc75707d5fae5ef98e1239cbec1')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 56というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/44/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/44/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d26affc75707d5fae5ef98e1239cbec1"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/4\/44\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/4\/44\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-56-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">冷水で髪をすすぎます。</b>水が冷たいほど効果が高くなります。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1656">
<a name="step_17_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-57-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 57というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/65/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="250f2e05287681ffae35d24ec27d3e04" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/65/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('250f2e05287681ffae35d24ec27d3e04')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 57というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/65/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/65/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="250f2e05287681ffae35d24ec27d3e04"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/6\/65\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/6\/65\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-57-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">モルトビネガーと白ワインビネガーを1：1の割合で混ぜます。</b>この混合液と水を1：1の割合で混ぜます。できあがりが70～100ミリリットルになるように調整します。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1657">
<a name="step_17_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-58-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 58というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="c2265f324586f8f13d13472762c07de9" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('c2265f324586f8f13d13472762c07de9')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 58というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="c2265f324586f8f13d13472762c07de9"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/e3\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/e3\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-58-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">髪から水が滴り落ちない程度で十分に濡れたら、この混合液を頭の上からかけます。</b>頭皮と髪全体に行き渡るように、しっかりとすり込みます。5～10分おきます。わずかに肌を刺すような感触がしばらくありますが、フケの原因となる、死んだ頭皮の細胞を取り除いているところです。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1658">
<a name="step_17_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-59-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 59というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="da0761d3ee9ea5d8d786d885ba3ab331" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('da0761d3ee9ea5d8d786d885ba3ab331')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 59というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="da0761d3ee9ea5d8d786d885ba3ab331"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/2\/24\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/2\/24\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-59-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">冷水で丁寧に洗い流します。</b>混合液が残らないように頭皮をしっかりと洗います。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1659">
<a name="step_17_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-60-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 60というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="613a8a73e327d0db4483c1ce0ae39af8" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('613a8a73e327d0db4483c1ce0ae39af8')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 60というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/24/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="613a8a73e327d0db4483c1ce0ae39af8"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/2\/24\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/2\/24\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-60-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">重曹大さじ1/2を用意します。</b>30～40ミリリットルの水と混ぜ、軽く泡立てます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1660">
<a name="step_17_6" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-61-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 61というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fc41434f4415c1ec6bc130e8fd474441" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/6c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('fc41434f4415c1ec6bc130e8fd474441')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 61というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/6c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fc41434f4415c1ec6bc130e8fd474441"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/6\/6c\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/6\/6c\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-61-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">6</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">髪が十分に濡れて、かつ水がしたたり落ちない状態であることを確認して、混合液を頭の上からかけます。</b>頭皮と髪全体に行き渡るようにしっかりとすり込みます。3～5分おきます。肌を刺すような感触が少しあります。酢の混合液の時よりその感触が早く強く訪れるかもしれませんが、これも、フケの原因となる、死んだ頭皮の細胞を取り除いているところです。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1661">
<a name="step_17_7" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-62-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 62というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/53/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="33a8c35dcfcce2bfeab9c4bbf0476865" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/53/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('33a8c35dcfcce2bfeab9c4bbf0476865')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 62というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/53/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/53/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="33a8c35dcfcce2bfeab9c4bbf0476865"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/5\/53\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/5\/53\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-62-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">7</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">冷水で丁寧に洗い流します。</b>頭皮をしっかりと洗います。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1662">
<a name="step_17_8" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-63-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 63というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/99/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1a7d84184e856e2586d0197cf969de6b" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/99/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('1a7d84184e856e2586d0197cf969de6b')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 63というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/99/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/99/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1a7d84184e856e2586d0197cf969de6b"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/9\/99\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/9\/99\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-63-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">8</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">タオルで優しく髪を拭きます。</b>自然乾燥させます。髪が乾いたら頭を下に向けて指でゆっくりと髪をすきます。何かしらの薄片が残っていれば、髪をこすり合わせて落とします。これでもうフケはありません。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
