<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>18</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ヨーグルト"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.A8.E3.83.BC.E3.82.B0.E3.83.AB.E3.83.88"><div class="method_label">方法 18 の 24:</div>ヨーグルト</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_18" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1763">
<a name="step_18_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-64-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 64というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="8be03a146a602adae5ab824174260472" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/9f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('8be03a146a602adae5ab824174260472')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 64というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/9f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="8be03a146a602adae5ab824174260472"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/9\/9f\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/9\/9f\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-64-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">普段通りに髪を洗い、よくすすいでからプレーンヨーグルトを頭皮にすり込み、10～15分おきます。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1764">
<a name="step_18_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-65-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 65というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/05/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="411aef97f073c95bb7523e988db8d6c6" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/05/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('411aef97f073c95bb7523e988db8d6c6')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 65というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/05/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/05/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="411aef97f073c95bb7523e988db8d6c6"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/05\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/05\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-65-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ヨーグルトを洗い流してから、できるだけ少量のシャンプーで洗髪します。</b>タイム、ネトル、またはセージを煎じて、大さじ2杯の酢を加えた液を仕上げのすすぎに使うことができます。フレッシュハーブ、または乾燥ハーブをお茶パックに入れるか、またはそのままお湯に浸して煎じます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1765">
<a name="step_18_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-66-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 66というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="25b9ff7a92e794bc9b52dd0dbbae53dc" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/7f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('25b9ff7a92e794bc9b52dd0dbbae53dc')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 66というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/7f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7f/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="25b9ff7a92e794bc9b52dd0dbbae53dc"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/7f\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/7f\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-66-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ティーポットを温め、カップ1杯につき小さじ1杯のハーブを入れます。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1766">
