<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 67というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="3a1f683bde9619d98fd2e0be47756e9e" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('3a1f683bde9619d98fd2e0be47756e9e')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 67というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="3a1f683bde9619d98fd2e0be47756e9e"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f6\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f6\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-67-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">カップ分の熱湯を注ぎます。</b>10～15分おいて、残っているヨーグルトを洗い流します。余ったハーブティーを頭皮にかけると、さらに頭皮の状態が良くなります。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
