<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>19</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ニームとオリーブオイル"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.8B.E3.83.BC.E3.83.A0.E3.81.A8.E3.82.AA.E3.83.AA.E3.83.BC.E3.83.96.E3.82.AA.E3.82.A4.E3.83.AB"><div class="method_label">方法 19 の 24:</div>ニームとオリーブオイル</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_19" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1867">
<a name="step_19_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-68-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 68というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="00559574c6dc55e2f739ffc5ddb55080" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/00/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('00559574c6dc55e2f739ffc5ddb55080')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 68というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/00/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="00559574c6dc55e2f739ffc5ddb55080"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/00\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/00\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-68-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ヒマラヤニームカプセルを2～4個用意します。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1868">
<a name="step_19_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-69-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 69というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="2b90868191e80213c27b9f8bd24b79f9" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('2b90868191e80213c27b9f8bd24b79f9')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 69というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/73/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="2b90868191e80213c27b9f8bd24b79f9"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/73\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/73\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-69-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">カプセルを割り、中身を取り出します。</b>中には粗い粉末状のニームが入っています。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1869">
<a name="step_19_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-70-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
