</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 70というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c0/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c0/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d00c21b8779320c37931a2c4f6137835"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/c0\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/c0\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-70-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">オリーブオイル、または好みのオイルを大さじ４杯用意します。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1870">
<a name="step_19_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-71-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
