<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>20</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ムルタニミッティ"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.A0.E3.83.AB.E3.82.BF.E3.83.8B.E3.83.9F.E3.83.83.E3.83.86.E3.82.A3"><div class="method_label">方法 20 の 24:</div>ムルタニミッティ</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_20" class="section_text">
<p class="steps_text healthintro">ムルタニミッティは肌によいと言われ、インドで昔から使われている白い泥の粉末です。これは髪と頭皮のケアにも最適です。ムルタニミッティには冷却効果があり、余分な油を吸収し、頭皮の炎症を鎮めてフケを抑えます。
</p>
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-1972">
<a name="step_20_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-73-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 73というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a4e5c23d5f2e78ca976368126d555aec" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/7c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('a4e5c23d5f2e78ca976368126d555aec')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 73というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/7c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7c/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a4e5c23d5f2e78ca976368126d555aec"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/7c\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/7c\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-73-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">水とムルタニミッティを混ぜてペースト状にし、レモン果汁を加えます。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1973">
<a name="step_20_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-74-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 74というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/23/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="975514decbc0ea774dd3ac8cb25f368d" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/23/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('975514decbc0ea774dd3ac8cb25f368d')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 74というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/2/23/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/23/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="975514decbc0ea774dd3ac8cb25f368d"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/2\/23\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/2\/23\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-74-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">髪と頭皮に塗ります。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-1974">
<a name="step_20_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-75-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 75というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/ea/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dfef3f73124556f1f537147614d820fd" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/ea/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('dfef3f73124556f1f537147614d820fd')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 75というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/ea/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/ea/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dfef3f73124556f1f537147614d820fd"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/ea\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/ea\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-75-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">20分ほどおいてから水で洗い流します。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="wh_ad_inner w_label al_grey" data-service="adsense" data-slot="6771527778" data-width="728" data-height="90" data-smallheight="250" data-type="method" data-small="1" data-medium="1" data-channels="8788556287" data-mobilechannels="" data-largechannels="" data-smallchannels="" data-observerloading="1" data-sizes-array="0" data-gptdisplaylate="1">
<div id="mobilemethod_ad_20"></div>
<div class="al_method">広告</div>
</div>
