<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>21</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="エッグオイル"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.82.A8.E3.83.83.E3.82.B0.E3.82.AA.E3.82.A4.E3.83.AB"><div class="method_label">方法 21 の 24:</div>エッグオイル</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_21" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-2075">
<a name="step_21_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-76-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 76というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ce/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="584c7fb357a1c3ffbaa28ea602c4c30c" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ce/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('584c7fb357a1c3ffbaa28ea602c4c30c')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 76というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ce/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ce/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="584c7fb357a1c3ffbaa28ea602c4c30c"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/ce\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/ce\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-76-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">エッグオイルを頭皮に揉みこむように5～10分マッサージをし、そのまま一晩おきます。</b>エッグオイルには次のような成分が含まれています。
<ul>
<li>毛包細胞を活性化するドコサヘキサエン酸（DHA）などの長鎖不飽和オメガ３脂肪酸。</li>
<li>髪に艶と輝きを与え、フケを抑えるコレステロール。</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2076">
<a name="step_21_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-77-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 77というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="7929459d268706cddb6de293b32f5ee2" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('7929459d268706cddb6de293b32f5ee2')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 77というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e3/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="7929459d268706cddb6de293b32f5ee2"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/e3\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/e3\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-77-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">翌朝、刺激の少ない、できればハーブ系のシャンプーでオイルを洗い流します。</b>泡立たないからといって繰り返し洗うと、髪と頭皮の自然な水分が奪われ、乾燥して傷つきやすくなるので、シャンプーは1度だけにします。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2077">
<a name="step_21_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-78-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 78というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="449150819e7c3d4f35fba371af20a4bc" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/5a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('449150819e7c3d4f35fba371af20a4bc')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 78というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/5a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5a/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="449150819e7c3d4f35fba371af20a4bc"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/5\/5a\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/5\/5a\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-78-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">はっきりとした効果が現れるまで、エッグオイルを週に2～3回使用し、少なくとも12週間は続けましょう。</b>毛包細胞に十分な養分を与えるには、定期的に続けることが大切です。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2078">
<a name="step_21_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-79-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 79というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/80/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="288c99a4f48a6542d81b0f8fa79d7972" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/80/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('288c99a4f48a6542d81b0f8fa79d7972')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 79というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/80/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/80/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="288c99a4f48a6542d81b0f8fa79d7972"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/8\/80\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/8\/80\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-79-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">フケが再び出ないように、エッグオイルマッサージを長期間続けます。</b>
<ul><li>エッグオイルは使いやすく劣化の心配もありません。卵黄を使ってフケに対処するよりもはるかに簡単で、生卵独特の臭いもなく、また、熱いシャワーのせいで髪の中で固まる心配もありません。感染症を引き起こすサルモネラ菌の危険もありません。</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
