<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>22</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ココナッツと蜂蜜の頭皮スクラブ"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.82.B3.E3.82.B3.E3.83.8A.E3.83.83.E3.83.84.E3.81.A8.E8.9C.82.E8.9C.9C.E3.81.AE.E9.A0.AD.E7.9A.AE.E3.82.B9.E3.82.AF.E3.83.A9.E3.83.96"><div class="method_label">方法 22 の 24:</div>ココナッツと蜂蜜の頭皮スクラブ</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_22" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-2179">
<a name="step_22_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-80-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 80というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f5/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="f5835b995e3b3f054b6dd2d3af971474" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f5/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('f5835b995e3b3f054b6dd2d3af971474')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 80というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f5/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f5/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="f5835b995e3b3f054b6dd2d3af971474"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f5\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f5\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-80-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ココナッツオイル、オリーブオイル、ヨーグルト、蜂蜜を混ぜます。</b>4つの材料をおよそ2：2：3：2の割合で混ぜ、頭から流れ落ちない程度の滑らかなペーストにします。ゆる過ぎる場合にはヨーグルトと蜂蜜を加えます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2180">
<a name="step_22_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-81-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 81というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/ad/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="364c600d18bd769812cf6145ec24b8d7" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/ad/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('364c600d18bd769812cf6145ec24b8d7')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 81というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/ad/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/ad/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="364c600d18bd769812cf6145ec24b8d7"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/a\/ad\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/ad\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-81-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ペーストを頭皮にすり込みます。</b>髪の根元から毛先まで、時間をかけてまんべんなくペーストを伸ばします。10分ほど行います。こうすると、頭皮の毛穴が開いて血液の循環が促進されます。おまけに、とても気持ちがいいものです。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2181">
<a name="step_22_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-82-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 82というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/fc/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e5707fcb5e71878eb4bc8288fa3e50e3" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/fc/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('e5707fcb5e71878eb4bc8288fa3e50e3')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 82というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/fc/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/fc/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e5707fcb5e71878eb4bc8288fa3e50e3"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/fc\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/fc\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-82-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">湿度の高い所で20分馴染ませます。</b>ヘアースチーマーをかけてペーストを浸透させます。ヘアースチーマーがなければ、湯船につかりながら浸透させます。湯船がなくても、少し長めに（30～45分）おけばいいので心配ありません。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2182">
<a name="step_22_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-83-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 83というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e7f8cb66ce7a3398147364d92935cb7a" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('e7f8cb66ce7a3398147364d92935cb7a')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 83というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f6/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e7f8cb66ce7a3398147364d92935cb7a"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f6\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f6\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-83-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">頭皮からペーストがきれいに落ちるまでシャンプーで洗います。</b>お風呂場に入り髪を洗いましょう。通常、髪に付いたペーストを完全に落とすには2度洗いの必要があります。ただし、洗い過ぎないように気を付けましょう。洗い過ぎると、ペーストが与えた潤いが頭皮から奪われます。最後に、普段使用しているコンディショナーを毛先にだけ付けます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2183">
<a name="step_22_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-84-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 84というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="4a3fd29edd6760a36cd0a70bbecd47a1" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('4a3fd29edd6760a36cd0a70bbecd47a1')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 84というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="4a3fd29edd6760a36cd0a70bbecd47a1"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f9\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f9\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-84-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ドライヤーを使う際は「弱」にセットします。</b>ドライヤーによる乾いた熱風は、粉っぽい、フケ症の原因となります。普段、ドライヤーで髪をセットしているのであれば、熱風が直接頭皮にあたらないように気を付けながら髪をブローします。または、ストレートアイロンを普段使用しているのであれば、それで髪を整えます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2184">
<a name="step_22_6" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-85-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 85というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4d/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1a802f86367e015f34d1570a43a26c93" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/4d/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('1a802f86367e015f34d1570a43a26c93')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 85というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/4d/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4d/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1a802f86367e015f34d1570a43a26c93"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/4\/4d\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/4\/4d\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-85-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">6</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">仕上げに、ココナッツオイルで艶をだします。</b>手のひらに4～5滴ココナッツオイルを垂らし、両手を揉み合わせてココナッツオイルを温めます。両手を髪に通しながらオイルを髪と頭皮に馴染ませます。頭皮全体に行き渡るまで、必要であれば繰り返します。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="wh_ad_inner w_label al_grey" data-service="adsense" data-slot="6771527778" data-width="728" data-height="90" data-smallheight="250" data-type="method" data-small="1" data-medium="1" data-channels="8788556287" data-mobilechannels="" data-largechannels="" data-smallchannels="" data-observerloading="1" data-sizes-array="0" data-gptdisplaylate="1">
