<div class="clearall"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>23</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="オレンジの皮パック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.82.AA.E3.83.AC.E3.83.B3.E3.82.B8.E3.81.AE.E7.9A.AE.E3.83.91.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 23 の 24:</div>オレンジの皮パック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_23" class="section_text">
<p class="steps_text healthintro">オレンジに含まれるビタミンCとクエン酸には、体の調子を整え、肌をきれいにする働きがあります。また、オレンジの皮はヘアケアに効果があります。オレンジの皮に含まれる酸には、過剰な油分を抑える性質があります。オレンジの皮の性質を利用した、家庭でも簡単にできるフケの対処法は次の通りです。
</p>
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-2285">
<a name="step_23_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-86-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 86というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="7921ff52831d5a32f4900e1fc10035c5" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('7921ff52831d5a32f4900e1fc10035c5')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff (Natural Methods) Step 86というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c9/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="7921ff52831d5a32f4900e1fc10035c5"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/c9\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/c9\/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-%28Natural-Methods%29-Step-86-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">レモン果汁とオレンジの皮をミキサーで混ぜてペーストを作ります。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2286">
<a name="step_23_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-(Natural-Methods)-Step-87-Version-2.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
