<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>24</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="塩"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.A1.A9"><div class="method_label">方法 24 の 24:</div>塩</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_24" class="section_text">
<p class="steps_text healthintro">塩には血液の循環を促進して健康的な頭皮を保つとともに、フケを浮かせて取り除く働きがあります。また、余分な油分と水分を吸収して菌類の増殖を防ぎ、フケの発生を止めます。家庭でできる、
塩を使った簡単なフケの対処方は次の通りです。
</p>
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-2389">
<a name="step_24_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff Fast Step 2というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/11/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0ba212cfcc97374e66b41ea763ca489d" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/11/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('0ba212cfcc97374e66b41ea763ca489d')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Get Rid of Dandruff Fast Step 2というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/11/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/11/Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Rid-of-Dandruff-Fast-Step-2-Version-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0ba212cfcc97374e66b41ea763ca489d"></noscript>
