<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">髪を何度か分けます。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2390">
<a name="step_24_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Lighten-Your-Hair-Naturally-Step-4-Version-3.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
