<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">小さじ1～2杯の塩を頭皮に振りかけます。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-2391">
<a name="step_24_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Comb-Long-Hair-Step-1-Version-4.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
