<b class="whb">2～3分マッサージをします。</b>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li class="final_li" id="step-id-2392">
<a name="step_24_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Get-Good-Looking-Hair-(Milk-Conditioning)-Step-9.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Get Good Looking Hair (Milk Conditioning) Step 9というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/61/Get-Good-Looking-Hair-%28Milk-Conditioning%29-Step-9.jpg/v4-728px-Get-Good-Looking-Hair-%28Milk-Conditioning%29-Step-9.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="94d34b4a7f2022ad1ee4d03e25dd6066" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/61/Get-Good-Looking-Hair-%28Milk-Conditioning%29-Step-9.jpg/v4-460px-Get-Good-Looking-Hair-%28Milk-Conditioning%29-Step-9.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('94d34b4a7f2022ad1ee4d03e25dd6066')</script>
